1092
01:05:30,830 --> 01:05:31,860
She was special.

1093
01:05:33,030 --> 01:05:35,620
Yeah, she was special, Daisy.

1094
01:05:37,110 --> 01:05:38,460
Not easy.

1095
01:05:40,510 --> 01:05:42,220
